tre Seigneur S'est prescrit \u00e0 Lui-m\u00eame la mis\u00e9ricorde. Et quiconque d'entre vous a fait un mal par ignorance, et ensuite s'est repenti et s'est r\u00e9form\u00e9... Il est, alors, Pardonneur et Mis\u00e9ricordieux\".","spell":"Wa-idzaa jaa-akal-ladziina yu'minuuna biaayaatinaa faqul salaamun 'alaikum kataba rabbukum 'ala nafsihirrahmata annahu man 'amila minkum suu-an bijahaalatin tsumma taaba min ba'dihi wa-ashlaha fa-annahu ghafuurun rahiimun"},{"arabic":"\u0665\u0665.  \t\u0648\u064e\u0643\u064e\u0630\u064e\u0670\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064e \u0646\u064f\u0641\u064e\u0635\u0651\u0650\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0622\u064a\u064e\u0627\u062a\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0644\u0650\u062a\u064e\u0633\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0646\u064e \u0633\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u062c\u0652\u0631\u0650\u0645\u0650\u064a\u0646\u064e","english":"55.  \tAnd thus do We explain the Ay\u00e2t (proofs, evidences, verses, lessons, signs, revelations, etc.) in detail, that the way of the Mujrim\u00fbn (criminals, polytheists, sinners), may become manifest.","indonesian":"55. Dan demikianlah Kami terangkan ayat-ayat Al-Quran (supaya jelas jalan orang-orang yang saleh, dan supaya jelas (pula) jalan orang-orang yang berdosa.","japanese":"55. &#12371;&#12398;&#12424;&#12358;&#12395;&#12431;&#12428;&#12399;&#65292;&#21360;&#12434;&#35443;&#32048;&#12395;&#12431;&#12383;&#12387;&#12390;&#35299;&#26126;&#12375;&#12383;&#12290;&#12371;&#12428;&#12399;&#32618;&#12434;&#29359;&#12377;&#32773;&#12398;&#36799;&#12427;&#36947;&#12434;&#26126;&#31034;&#12377;&#12427;&#12383;&#12417;&#12391;&#12354;&#12427;&#12290;","korean":"55. \uadf8\ub9ac\ud558\uc5ec \ud558\ub098\ub2d8\uc774 \ub9d0\uc500\uc744 \uc790\uc138\ud788 \uc124\uba85\ud558\ub098\ub2c8 \uc774\ub294 \uc8c4\uc9c0\uc740 \uc790\ub4e4\uc758 \uae38\uc744 \ubc1d\ud600 \uc8fc\uace0\uc790 \ud568\uc774\ub77c","chinese":"55. \u6211\u9019\u6a23\u89e3\u91cb\u4e00\u5207\u8e5f\u8c61\uff0c\u4ee5\u4f